description: Faux tan went on a little too dark and now you're looking like an Oompa Loompa? Don't worry - all you need is the ModelCo Tan Remover Exfoliating Soap. Working with ease, it quickly removes old self-tan, streaks, stains and build-up - with no waiting required. It's enriched with goat's milk and a sweet coconut scent, and contains natural pumice to polish and exfoliate the skin. Working just as well on difficult areas like between the fingers and toes, this soap is a must-have for your beauty kit. Product Features:Removes old self-tan, streaks, stains and build-upWorks quicklyEnriched with goat's milkContains natural pumiceSweet coconut scentEffective on difficult areasContents: 125g
